  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  DisplayText: 'However, before you can even revel in your victory you feel blood
    start to drip from your chest. Valdris struck you too, another fatal blow. You
    lie down, you let the tears well up in your eyes for the first time since Asmund
    died. You did it, struck down at the last moment but you did it. You let the
    taste of victory consume your last moments, and you move on to Valhalla. '
